@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_reirpu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v0 + ((v0 + 0.47 * tmp + 0.10) / (v1 + 0.96 / v0 + 0.37)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.02 / v0 + 0.21)) + (wp.cos(v1 + 0.87) - (v2 + 0.31 * tmp + 0.26)))
    v2 = (v2 / (wp.sin(v0 + 0.92) * v2))
    v2 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.61) - (v0 + 0.83 / tmp + 0.11)) * 0.06)
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin(0.81))
    v0 = 0.92
    data[tid] = v0
